# Phonebook

## Introduction
A simple phonebook application


## Installation

Install dependencies

```sh
npm install
```

Launch the application in frontend directory

```sh
npm start
```

### Using JSON server as the server
Change baseUrl in client/src/services to "http://localhost:3001/persons"

Start json-server in frontend directory

```sh
npm run server
```

### Using MongoDB as the server
Note: change baseUrl in client/src/services to "api/persons"

Start MongoDB server in backend directory

```sh
npm run dev
```

